{"tid":801285,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"【新界水浸都係黃雨】一張圖解釋大交合所謂嘅「廣泛地區」標準","createTime":"2018-08-31T13:33:15.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-02T17:02:40.000Z","uid":91244,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"b7d80904f3076486518a7acfe28e645777a89a90","tid":801285,"uid":91244,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-31T13:33:15.000Z","msg":"作為一個氣象迷，（至少我）向來對大交合嘅態度都係是其是非其非。<br />\n今次暴雨惹黎嘅爭議，其實不外乎又係準則問題。講緊嘅準則係比我地氣象迷都屌左好L耐嘅所謂「廣泛地區」，「預料XX」同埋針對持續暴雨嘅處理手法。<br />\n今次想特別講交合近年好強調嘅「廣泛地區」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/31/205914_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F31%2F205914_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=e6dad452&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n（From MET WARN天氣預警）<br />\n<br />\n成日見人用交合最高得40mm嘅圖屌交合，老老77人地公開得比你睇邊有咁易有痛腳捉。<br />\n上面張圖已經解釋到點解8.26果次港島紅雨可以出得咁當機立斷，而8.29果次就拖咁耐。<br />\n<br />\n簡單啲講，交合出雨警除左睇夠唔夠每小時30/50/70mm之外（少於1小時/多於2小時有另外標準），仲會根據達標雨量站嘅站數去決定係咪符合「廣泛地區」。<br />\n而問題就黎啦，張圖顯示嘅雨量計，當中有一部份係天文台嘅參考站，而明顯地港島嘅站數比例同新界大部份新市鎮/已發展區域係完全唔成正比。換句話講，如果個雨區落正港九，自自然然就好快會數夠站繼而出返相應暴雨警告，亦即係8.26港島紅雨嘅情況。而8.29新界暴雨亦都因為雨量站疏落嘅緣故，而令到落左一段時間嘅狗屎先至數夠站數出紅雨。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/31/212503_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F31%2F212503_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=556a48cc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n（我記得張圖好似係連登巴打整但唔記得係邊位<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ）<br />\n<br />\n呢樣野係氣象界真係比人屌左好多年，現行嘅暴雨準則已經行左廿年。廿年黎新界不斷發展，人口數量/密度絕對不亞於市區，到底交合幾時先正視呢個問題呢？定係又要整多鑊92年5月8日嘅大暴雨（但齋係新界）先肯改革？"},{"pid":"17e17e15edba61b45786d851893ea4753a83d618","tid":801285,"uid":205862,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-01T15:32:58.000Z","msg":"pish 到大交合回應"},{"pid":"59b4094433464718c831ddecd93a74686dca589b","tid":801285,"uid":120791,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-01T15:34:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a4e854181fc24207c28a9518a619f87f47d6dbb4","tid":801285,"uid":153531,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-01T15:34:55.000Z","msg":"港島&gt;九龍新界<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d9fbec1a4dc1e59f3ca8df0d87b3699d517c2ab8","tid":801285,"uid":135274,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-01T15:38:05.000Z","msg":"其實就算係受制於其他政府部門搞到擺唔到筒（張圖都見到大部分筒都唔係大交合擺），都可以搞加權平均呢啲數據處理既方法，所以大交合根本係責無旁貸 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1a3ad4765e82ffda439c338bad36535c95ba4400","tid":801285,"uid":166706,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-01T15:55:49.000Z","msg":"香港政府做野傳統不嬲唔撞板唔識改<br />\n當年派比安襲港，大交合死都話維港風力未達標，後來比人屌到上天花先識改<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"55b078a4b4453654efb00662af250d401a5dd64f","tid":801285,"uid":6293,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-01T17:34:31.000Z","msg":"其實宣傳大交合玩分裂佢地會唔會極速回應<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4a70d41290f9aa81b00b105295703e71c32aeff5","tid":801285,"uid":38255,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"17e17e15edba61b45786d851893ea4753a83d618","tid":801285,"uid":205862,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-01T15:32:58.000Z","msg":"pish 到大交合回應"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-01T17:49:02.000Z","msg":"其實要拉埋土木工程處出黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 大部份雨量計都係佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9cd75aece61c895bd467f257d253063a279993cc","tid":801285,"uid":205862,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4a70d41290f9aa81b00b105295703e71c32aeff5","tid":801285,"uid":38255,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"17e17e15edba61b45786d851893ea4753a83d618","tid":801285,"uid":205862,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-01T15:32:58.000Z","msg":"pish 到大交合回應"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-01T17:49:02.000Z","msg":"其實要拉埋土木工程處出黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 大部份雨量計都係佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-01T18:16:03.000Z","msg":"其實大交合參考咩數據出警係佢地自己決定，唔應該拉其他部門落水"},{"pid":"44b0cd30f84d0de1fd2a8355b97abe29365c9499","tid":801285,"uid":91244,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-02T16:47:50.000Z","msg":"其實以上列出嘅雨量計，只有一部份屬於大交合參考雨量站。<br />\n而個refernce base之中，唔可以排除新界水浸黑點或者新界新市鎮嘅參考站數量比起上圖更加疏落。"},{"pid":"c6fe3c278e99d34addcd49931d3c81493ef211c7","tid":801285,"uid":38255,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"44b0cd30f84d0de1fd2a8355b97abe29365c9499","tid":801285,"uid":91244,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-02T16:47:50.000Z","msg":"其實以上列出嘅雨量計，只有一部份屬於大交合參考雨量站。<br />\n而個refernce base之中，唔可以排除新界水浸黑點或者新界新市鎮嘅參考站數量比起上圖更加疏落。"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-02T16:52:06.000Z","msg":"所以改善方法有兩種<br />\n<br />\n一丶減少港島雨量筒分佈至新界九龍水平<br />\n二、增加新界九龍雨量筒分佈至港島水平<br />\n<br />\n一呢種魚蛋論明顯唔正確變左港九新界人命都一齊輕視<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n即係問題唔係得港島大雨就即紅雨而係得新界大雨唔即紅<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d016cb42d1e3fefa3199c12a1377f2179248991d","tid":801285,"uid":91244,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"d9fbec1a4dc1e59f3ca8df0d87b3699d517c2ab8","tid":801285,"uid":135274,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-01T15:38:05.000Z","msg":"其實就算係受制於其他政府部門搞到擺唔到筒（張圖都見到大部分筒都唔係大交合擺），都可以搞加權平均呢啲數據處理既方法，所以大交合根本係責無旁貸 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-02T16:53:42.000Z","msg":"最緊要大交合有無同其他部門協調<br />\n出泥警會同GEO協調共同出警<br />\n水浸固然唔係交合問題，係DSD責任（撇除支國排洪大禮等因素）<br />\n但出北水交合又會唔會重視DSD雨量計數據亦係重點"},{"pid":"f92462a73f10f0bd5543c4c2547721b479a4cbc2","tid":801285,"uid":91244,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c6fe3c278e99d34addcd49931d3c81493ef211c7","tid":801285,"uid":38255,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"44b0cd30f84d0de1fd2a8355b97abe29365c9499","tid":801285,"uid":91244,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-02T16:47:50.000Z","msg":"其實以上列出嘅雨量計，只有一部份屬於大交合參考雨量站。<br />\n而個refernce base之中，唔可以排除新界水浸黑點或者新界新市鎮嘅參考站數量比起上圖更加疏落。"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-02T16:52:06.000Z","msg":"所以改善方法有兩種<br />\n<br />\n一丶減少港島雨量筒分佈至新界九龍水平<br />\n二、增加新界九龍雨量筒分佈至港島水平<br />\n<br />\n一呢種魚蛋論明顯唔正確變左港九新界人命都一齊輕視<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n即係問題唔係得港島大雨就即紅雨而係得新界大雨唔即紅<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-02T16:57:00.000Z","msg":"今年交合嘅做法同一呢種方法都好接近<br />\n無論港九新界都係實測性質黃雨多過預警性質<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7b4dc03382f34f91083ec63454e4e21009af663b","tid":801285,"uid":91244,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"1a3ad4765e82ffda439c338bad36535c95ba4400","tid":801285,"uid":166706,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-01T15:55:49.000Z","msg":"香港政府做野傳統不嬲唔撞板唔識改<br />\n當年派比安襲港，大交合死都話維港風力未達標，後來比人屌到上天花先識改<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-02T17:01:12.000Z","msg":"改完個8站都係笑話黎<br />\n不過林黑英肯改已經係奇蹟